title: Ep. - 329 - HEATHER GAY FROM REAL HOUSEWIVES OF SALT LAKE CITY DANNI BAIRD FROM SOUTHERN CHARM
description:
Heather Gay from Bravo’s Real Housewives of Salt Lake City talks about joining the show, opens up about struggle with her Mormon faith, and how the show has changed her life.

 

Danni Baird from Bravo’s Southern Charm talks about this season and the explosive reunion.
